example.para:
To make local address lookups for foobar.example.com resolve to the
      192.168.100.1 IPv4 address, create
      /run/systemd/resolve/static.d/foobar_example_com.rr:


{
        "key" : {
                "type" : 1,
                "name" : "foobar.example.com"
        },
        "address" : [ 192, 168, 100, 1 ]
}
